-card__text--p\">\n              Family of research in CE play a critical role in the construction\n              of infrastructure, infrastructure projects and costs and design\n              airports, bridges and the highways millions of people use.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"courses-card__text--link\"><a href=\"http://210.18.180.227/academics/courses/civil-engineering/\">know more</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"courses-card\">\n          <div class=\"courses-card__image\">\n            <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/themes/Sanskrithi/assets/img/Humanities and Science.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"courses-card__text\">\n            <h3 class=\"courses-card__text--h3\">Humanities Sciences</h3>\n            <p class=\"courses-card__text--p\">\n              The H&amp;S department vision is to pursues teaching, research and\n              service in the area of mathematics, physics chemistry and English.\n              The department is committed to high quality instruction for all\n              students.\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"courses-card__text--link\"><a href=\"http://210.18.180.227/academics/courses/humanities-and-science/\">know more</a></p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'All Courses', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'all-courses', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:56:40', '2022-07-11 10:56:40', '', 226, 'http://localhost/?page_id=240', 0, 'page', '', 0),
