(304, 1, '2022-07-07 07:42:39', '2022-07-07 07:42:39', '<!-- wp:html -->\n <p>\n          Ministry of Human Resource Development (MHRD), Govt. of India has\n          established ‘MHRD’s Innovation Cell (MIC)’ to systematically foster\n          the culture of Innovation amongst all Higher Education Institutions\n          (HEIs). The primary mandate of MIC is to encourage, inspire and\n          nurture young students by supporting them to work with new ideas and\n          transform them into prototypes. SSE IIC was established in 2020, to\n          promote innovation in the Institution through multitudinous modes\n          leading to an innovation promotion eco-system in the campuses.\n        </p>\n        <h3 class=\"committee-page-content__main--h3\">Major focus of IIC</h3>\n        <ul class=\"committee-page-content__main--ul\">\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            To create a vibrant local innovation ecosystem.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Start-up supporting Mechanism in HEIs\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Prepare institute for Atal Ranking of Institutions on Innovation\n            Achievements Framework.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Establish Function Ecosystem for Scouting Ideas and Pre-incubation\n            of Ideas.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Develop better Cognitive Ability for Technology Students.\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <h3 class=\"committee-page-content__main--h3\">Committee Members</h3>\n        <div class=\"committies-cards-container\">\n          <div class=\"committies-card\">\n            <h4 class=\"committies-card__title\">Chairperson</h4>\n            <h3>Dr Senthil Kumar A</h3>\n            <p>Principal</p>\n            <p>9100974518</p>\n        