(337, 1, '2022-07-07 08:50:53', '2022-07-07 08:50:53', '<!-- wp:html -->\n\n        <p>\n          Industry Institute Interaction cell acts as a bridge to share\n          expertise, experience and infrastructure between Industry & Institute.\n        </p>\n        <h3 class=\"committee-page-content__main--h3\">Functions</h3>\n        <ul class=\"committee-page-content__main--ul\">\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Facilitate Institute & Industry engagement through internships,\n            joint projects with industry, seminars, workshops, Industrial\n            visits, student exchange programs and placements.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Identify industry partners and proactively engage (tie-up) them to\n            explore opportunities in technical research.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Facilitate SDP (Student Development Program) & FDP (Faculty\n            Development Program) by inviting Industry Experts to give training\n            on Technical & Soft skills\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Act as a resource coordinator & provide mentor support to students\n            working in Mega project teams, E-Cell and Student bodies.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"committee-page-content__main--li\">\n            Facilitate and organize activities of Atal Ranking (ARIIA) and\n            Institution’s Innovation Council (IIC) - an initiative by MHRD\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n        <h3 class=\"committee-page-content__main--h3\">Committee Members</h3>\n        <div class=\"committies-cards-container\">\n          <div class=\"committies-card\">\n            <h4 class=\"committies-card__title\">Chairperson</h4>\n            <h3>Dr Bala Koteswari</h3>\n            <p>Dean</p>\n            <p>9100974516</p>\n            <p>principal@sankrith