(375, 1, '2022-07-07 12:03:45', '2022-07-07 12:03:45', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>\n          Sports and games are essential to develop the students physically as well as mentally.  They enhance the personality of individuals by imparting various traits in them. Sports boost alertness, disciple, team spirit, mental ability, confidence, and concentration of a student. It does not matter what kind of sports the students are playing and whether they are winning or not. Every sport will always inculcate some amazing traits in them.  SSE prides itself on encouraging sportsmanship. Basketball, cricket, volleyball facilities are present on the campus sports ground. Yoga and jogging sessions are conducted every morning. \n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Sports Ground', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sports-ground', '', '', '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '', 70, 'http://localhost/?page_id=375', 3, 'page', '', 0),
