(395, 1, '2022-07-11 10:02:50', '2022-07-11 10:02:50', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<h2>Vision</h2>\n        <p>\n          To develop dynamic and socially responsible engineers possessing\n          wisdom, positive attitude, and an impeccable character. Hallmarks will\n          be the innovation, initiative, and teamwork the ability to anticipate\n          and effectively respond to change and to create opportunities.\n        </p>\n\n        <h2>Mission</h2>\n        <ul class=\"inside-page-content__main--ul\">\n          <li class=\"inside-page-content__main--li\">\n            The college is devoted to serving the society and the nation by\n            providing quality education, and skill development programs thereby\n            enabling the students to become skilled engineers with the right\n            kind of knowledge.\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"inside-page-content__main--li\">\n            Committed towards setting new benchmarks of excellence in technical\n            education with emphasis on research &amp; development, innovation and\n            services to the society, industry, and the world.\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Vision and Mission', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '169-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:02:50', '2022-07-11 10:02:50', '', 169, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=395', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(397, 1, '2022-07-11 10:10:03', '2022-07-11 10:10:03', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"message-page-content__person\">\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--image\">\n          <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/themes/Sanskrithi/assets/img/Chairman Message.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--designation\">\n          <h2 class=\"person-name\">Vijay Reddy</h2>\n          <p class=\"person-designation\">Chairman, Sanskrithi Group</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"message-page-content__main\">\n        <p>Greetings from the Sanskrithi School OF Engineering- Puttaparthi.</p>\n        <p>\n          At the outset, let me first congratulate you all for opting for the\n          Engineering domain as your future career. This college is a part of\n          the group of institutions, we are developing under the banner of\n          “Sanskrithi Group.” At a time when engineering education is said to be\n          in doldrums in the state of AP, we have taken a bold step to bring the\n          glory back to the Engineering Profession with international standards\n          and industry-collaborations for excellence in education and employment\n          for the aspiring youth.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          The College is situated at Puttaparthi , the abode of Bhagawan Sri\n          Sathya Sai Baba, under whose inspiration and blessings I have started\n          these educational institutions back in 2010 and God has been kind to\n          us to give the absolute best in every endeavor we take up. SSE has\n          been the latest in our success story. At SSE we have created\n          world-class facilities for best of the best education in Engineering\n          with professionally qualified faculty and state-of the Art\n          laboratories and infrastructure.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          I\'m sure the young boys and girls who join this college will have\n          wonderful future in professional and personal life.\n        </p>\n        <p>With best wishes,</p>\n        <p>\n          <span class=\"bold-name\">VIJAY REDDY</span><br />\n          CHAIRMAN - SANSKRITHI GROUP\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Chairman Message', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '114-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:10:03', '2022-07-11 10:10:03', '', 114, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=397', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(398, 1, '2022-07-11 10:10:43', '2022-07-11 10:10:43', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"message-page-content__person\">\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--image\">\n          <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/themes/Sanskrithi/assets/img/dean Message.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--designation\">\n          <h2 class=\"person-name\">Dr. Bala Koteswari</h2>\n          <p class=\"person-designation\">Dean - Academics</p>\n          <p class=\"person-qualification\">\n            Ph.D., MBA, Msc., (Gold Medal) PGDHRM, B.Ed.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"message-page-content__main\">\n        <p>\n          It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you to Sanskrithi School of\n          Engineering. Choosing the right engineering program is one of the most\n          important decisions that you will make in your life. You must be sure\n          that you opt for the best and the latest. In an increasing global and\n          competitive economic environment, innovation in line with market\n          requirements is the key to ensuring professional success.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          Keeping in mind the challenges and uncertainties, it is essential to\n          select an engineering stream that aligns with your personal interest,\n          future goals and financial ability. With SSE, you needn\'t look further\n          as we pride ourselves in providing the best faculty, infrastructure,\n          international learning opportunities with transport and hostel and\n          100% placements assistance affordable to all.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          Our program is structured keeping in mind the constantly changing\n          practices and standards in engineering fields.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          I take this opportunity to wish you a bright promising future and to\n          guide you towards achieving your dreams and goals.\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Dean Message', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '206-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:10:43', '2022-07-11 10:10:43', '', 206, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=398', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(399, 1, '2022-07-11 10:11:04', '2022-07-11 10:11:04', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"message-page-content__person\">\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--image\">\n          <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/themes/Sanskrithi/assets/img/Dean Message.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--designation\">\n          <h2 class=\"person-name\">Dr. Bala Koteswari</h2>\n          <p class=\"person-designation\">Dean - Academics</p>\n          <p class=\"person-qualification\">\n            Ph.D., MBA, Msc., (Gold Medal) PGDHRM, B.Ed.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"message-page-content__main\">\n        <p>\n          It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you to Sanskrithi School of\n          Engineering. Choosing the right engineering program is one of the most\n          important decisions that you will make in your life. You must be sure\n          that you opt for the best and the latest. In an increasing global and\n          competitive economic environment, innovation in line with market\n          requirements is the key to ensuring professional success.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          Keeping in mind the challenges and uncertainties, it is essential to\n          select an engineering stream that aligns with your personal interest,\n          future goals and financial ability. With SSE, you needn\'t look further\n          as we pride ourselves in providing the best faculty, infrastructure,\n          international learning opportunities with transport and hostel and\n          100% placements assistance affordable to all.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          Our program is structured keeping in mind the constantly changing\n          practices and standards in engineering fields.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          I take this opportunity to wish you a bright promising future and to\n          guide you towards achieving your dreams and goals.\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Dean Message', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '206-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:11:04', '2022-07-11 10:11:04', '', 206, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=399', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(400, 1, '2022-07-11 10:12:52', '2022-07-11 10:12:52', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"message-page-content__person\">\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--image\">\n          <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/themes/Sanskrithi/assets/img/principal message.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"message-page-content__person--designation\">\n          <h2 class=\"person-name\">Dr. A. Senthil Kumar</h2>\n          <p class=\"person-designation\">Principal</p>\n          <p class=\"person-qualification\">\n            B.E., M.E., MBA., PGDVLSI., DISM., Ph.D. (IITR)., PDF (TUT, SA).,\n            Senior PDF (VSB-TUO, EUROPE)., PGPAI&ML (University of Texas,\n            Austin)\n          </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"message-page-content__main\">\n        <p>\n          I am incredibly happy with the progress that we have been making to\n          produce generations of well informed and ethics-oriented engineers. I\n          am positive that in times to come we will continue this journey with\n          elevated enthusiasm and persistently provide a platform of holistic\n          learning to the young generation of learners.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          We spare no efforts to make the educational experience of our students\n          meaningful and relevant to the socio-economic needs of the times & to\n          equip them to face the challenges of the future for leading the\n          society from the front, while ensuring that at the same time they are\n          enjoying their experience of learning.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          My very competent team of faculty strive to focus on every student,\n          monitor and mentor them, appreciate their achievement, and encourage\n          them to overcome their shortcomings. I urge all the parents and\n          faculty to create appropriate, meaningful, and participative learning\n          situations, inculcating life skills, instilling confidence and hope to\n          their students so that they are ready to not just survive but succeed\n          in the world.\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Principal Message', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '216-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-11 10:12:52', '2022-07-11 10:12:52', '', 216, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=400', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
