(568, 1, '2022-07-26 11:08:13', '2022-07-26 11:08:13', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>\n          SSE library is expressly designed to meet the academic and research\n          needs of the SSE students and faculty alike. A knowledge hub, it\n          provides access to various information resources ranging from the\n          latest engineering study books, textbooks, and audio-visual materials.\n          The library is moving towards the electronic resources such as\n          e-books, e-journals, and databases.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          The library is constantly being restocked with new books and materials\n          to help with reference, research, user guidance service, photocopy\n          services, placement guide and current events awareness.\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Library', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '369-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-26 11:08:13', '2022-07-26 11:08:13', '', 369, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=568', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(569, 1, '2022-07-26 11:09:25', '2022-07-26 11:09:25', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>\n          The campus is WIFI enabled and internet of 40mbps supports the\n          college’s internet requirements. More than 300 units of latest\n          workstation, scanners, laser printers or desk jet printers, close\n          circuit camera, multimedia projectors, digital camera to serve the\n          desk need of faculty, student’s computer center, classrooms,\n          examination hall, auditorium, library, and various administrative\n          offices. The institute also has digital classes with projector\n          systems.\n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'IT Infrastructure', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '373-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-26 11:09:25', '2022-07-26 11:09:25', '', 373, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=569', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(570, 1, '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>\n          Sports and games are essential to develop the students physically as well as mentally.  They enhance the personality of individuals by imparting various traits in them. Sports boost alertness, disciple, team spirit, mental ability, confidence, and concentration of a student. It does not matter what kind of sports the students are playing and whether they are winning or not. Every sport will always inculcate some amazing traits in them.  SSE prides itself on encouraging sportsmanship. Basketball, cricket, volleyball facilities are present on the campus sports ground. Yoga and jogging sessions are conducted every morning. \n        </p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Sports Ground', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '375-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '2022-07-26 11:10:40', '', 375, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=570', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
