(625, 1, '2022-08-09 02:15:14', '2022-08-09 02:15:14', '<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-mahendra.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr. Mahendra. M</h3>\n              <h4>HoD</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr. Mahendra received his MTech (CSE) from University Visvesvaraya\n              College of Engineering (UVCE), Bangalore, and B. Tech (CSE) from\n              Sidda Ganga Institute of Technology (SIT), Tumkur Currently he is\n              pursuing PhD in Computer Science &amp; Engineering from Sri\n              Chandrasekharan Saraswathi Viswa Maha Vidyalaya University\n              (SCSVMV). He has a teaching experience of 11 years. He has\n              published his research in many International, National Journals\n              and Conferences. His research interests include Data Mining,\n              Python, Information Security.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-paul-spiesberger.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr. Paul Spiesberger</h3>\n              <h4>Adjunct Professor, RIT Program</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Adjunct professor and creator of the SSE –RISE RIT Program, Paul\n              Spiesberger graduated as a computer scientist with focus on Media\n              from the Vienna University of Technology. He works as a researcher\n              and lecturer in the field of computer science with focus on mobile\n              technologies around the globe and is also employed as a software\n              developer for mobile technologies within RISE, a fast-growing\n              European company. In the past he won several national and\n              international awards for his work. Since 2014 Paul is the\n              chairperson of ICT4D.at – the Austrian Network for Information and\n              Communication Technologies for Development and engages himself in\n              his spare time by using his skills also, for the common good.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/paul-spiesberger-09258a1b6/?originalSubdomain=at\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-raimund.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr Raimund Rittnauer</h3>\n              <h4>Adjunct Professor, RIT Program</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr. Raimund Rittnauer is a programming enthusiast having ten years\n              of experience programming C# at a company in Europe. Besides his\n              job as a software developer, he studies Business Informatics at\n              the Vienna University of Technology. In due course of his work, he\n              has created numerous web applications for Austrian companies and\n              events. He visits India as an Adjunct Faculty to SSE via the\n              IAESTE Faculty Exchange Program, where he has been working with\n              the institution in creating and continuing an hands-on course on\n              par with international standards.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/rittnauer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-noor-mohammad.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr. Noor Mohammed</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr. Noor Mohammed received his MTech degree in CSE from Maharshi\n              Dayanand University, Rohtak, B. Tech from JNTU Hyderabad with\n              First Division. He has a teaching experience of more than 12\n              years. He has published papers ,8 in international journals and 2\n              in National journals. His research interests include Information\n              Security. He has organized numerous Faculty Development Programs\n              and Training Programs. Currently pursuing PhD\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/noor-mohammed-7961769b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-adarsha.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr. Adarsha. S P</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr. Adarsha S P received his MTech and BTech in CSE from VTU,\n              Bangalore. He has teaching experience of more than 5 years. He has\n              published in various International, National Journals and\n              Conferences. His research interests include Python, AI, Machine\n              Learning, and Information Security. As the member of SGI Training\n              &amp; Placements Cell, he is the Engineering Placements coordinator\n              and SSE liaison for the RIT Program.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/adarshasp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n     