puter Science and Engineering from SVU\n              Tirupathi in the year 2013, and post graduated in computer science\n              and engineering from JNTUH Hyderabad in the year 2017. He has 3+\n              years\' experience in teaching. He has published 1 international\n              journal and presented the paper in the international conferences.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/maruthi-maru-5a763093\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-lakxmiprasanna.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Ms Lakshmi Prasanna</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Graduated in Information Technology from JNTUH in 2004, and post\n              graduated in Computer Science from MDU Rothak. She has 10 years of\n              teaching experience. Has published 2 National and 3 international\n              journals.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/cse-yuvarajnaik.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr Yuvaraj Naik. M</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr Yuvraj graduated in Computer Science and Engineering from\n              JNTUACEP in the year 2017, and post graduated in computer science\n              and engineering from JNTUA Ananthapuramu in the year 2019. He has\n              published in two international journals and presented the paper in\n              the international Conference.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/in/yuvaraj-naik-m-b01190246#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/profile-placeholder-200x200-1.png\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Tejaswini</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p></p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              