ation from JNTU college of Engineering and Bachelor of\n              Technology from BITS College of Engineering, Shivamogga,\n              Bengaluru. He has published 2 International Journal papers in\n              IRJET attended three national conferences. He has 5 years of\n              teaching experience.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ram-anji-5050a6218\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/civil-rammohan.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>G. Rammohon</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              G. Ram Mohan completed his MTech in Environmental Engineering\n              specialization from Sri Venkateshwara College of Engineering,\n              Tirupati from 2017 to 2019 and his Bachelor of Technology from Sri\n              Vidyaniketan College of Engineering, Tirupathi. He has published 5\n              International Journal papers attended five national conferences.\n              Has 4 years of teaching experience.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ram-mohan-76728a1a1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/profile-placeholder-200x200-1.png\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr Parthiban</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr Parthiban completed his ME in Structural Engineering in 2016\n              from Arunai Engineering College, Tiruvannamalai, affiliated to\n              Anna University Chennai. He has published over 7 papers on various\n              topics in National and International Jounrnals. He is also member\n              in the Indian Society of Technical Education (LM 117366, 2017) and\n              the International Association of Engineers ( LM 294869, 2021). Has\n              over 7 years of teaching experience.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/parthi-annadurai-0b5951111\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/civil-manjula.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Ms Manjula Bai K</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Ms. Manjula did her M. Tech with specialization in Structural\n              Engineering from MV Jayaram College of Engineering, Bangalore. Has\n              published 2 Journal papers in IRJET attended two national\n              conferences. She has experience of 3 years in teaching field.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/manjula-bai-k-250840125\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/civil-smitha.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Smitha GP</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Smitha GP has completed her MTech in Transportation Engineering\n              specialization and B Tech from JNNC College of Engineering,\n              Shivamogga, Bengaluru. She has published 5 International Journal\n              papers in IRJET attended three national conferences. She has 3\n              years teaching experience.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/smitha-gp-aa4501217\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-conten