    Associate Professor in the Department of Electronics and\n              Communication Engineering. He has over 15 years of teaching\n              experience and taught around 10 different subjects at\n              Undergraduate level. He published 8 Papers in various reputed\n              Journals, National and International Conferences and attended\n              various workshops and FDPs. His area of interest includes\n              Microwave Engineering, cellular and mobile communication, computer\n              networks, wireless video communications.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/devajji-nagaraju-22213116\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Ms. Pranavi N</h3>\n              <h4>Associate Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Obtained her B. Tech Degree (ECE) from SITS, Tirupathi and MTech\n              Degree in VLSI Design from SVEW, Tirupathi. She is doing her PhD\n              at KL University, Vijayawada. She has published her work in 3\n              International Journals and organized many seminars and workshops\n              and guided for UG projects. She is familiar with Xilinx and MATLAB\n              programming\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/pranavi-nachu-414662217\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr B Venkatesh</h3>\n              <h4>Assistant Professor</h4>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr Venkatesu has 14 years of teaching experience. He obtained his\n              M. Tech from Holy Mary Institute of Technology, and B. Tech He has\n              more than 10 publications published in national and international\n              journals.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/venkatesu-badisam-b255a8218\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr S Sadiq Vali</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr.Sadiqvali completed MTech in VLSI Design from JNTU Anantapuramu\n              and has 2 years of teaching experience in areas of interest\n              Digital Electronics, Embedded systems , Radar systems &amp; Control\n              Systems. He has published 3 papers in UGC Authorized journals.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Vijayramaraju R</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p></p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"lilink\">\n            <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n              <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n                <img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"linkedin link\">\n              </div>\n              <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n            </a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"faculty-member\">\n          <div class=\"faculty-member__photo\">\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--photo\">\n              <img src=\"\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"faculty-member__photo--name\">\n              <h3>Mr Jagadeesh S</h3>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faculty-member-description\">\n            <p>\n              Mr. Jagadeesh completed M.Tech in (VLSI system design) from\n              Sreenivasa Institute of Technology. Areas of interest include VLSI\n              desig