         wonderful future in professional and personal life.\n        </p>\n        <p>With best wishes,</p>\n        <p>\n          <span class=\"bold-name\">VIJAY REDDY</span><br />\n          CHAIRMAN - SANSKRITHI GROUP\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          <a href=\"mailto:chairman@sanskrithibschool.com\"\n            >chairman@sanskrithibschool.com</a\n          >\n        </p>\n<div class=\"lilink\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/vijay-reddy-bhaskar-29a3b95a\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"lilink__logo\">\n              <img src=\"http://210.18.180.227/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" />\n            </div>\n            <p>LinkedIn&nbsp;Profile</p>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'Chairman Message', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '114-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-08-16 17:26:08', '2022-08-16 17:26:08', '', 114, 'http://210.18.180.227/?p=732', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
